9
00:01:52,640 --> 00:01:54,500
Hey, can you just shut your mouth?

10
00:01:54,840 --> 00:01:55,680
Come on,

11
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:01,840
bro,

12
00:02:01,840 --> 00:02:03,360
let's go out for a drink.

13
00:02:03,360 --> 00:02:04,000
Shut up.

14
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,480
Or tomorrow,

15
00:02:06,480 --> 00:02:08,880
