16
00:02:08,880 --> 00:02:09,840
Get lost.

17
00:02:15,400 --> 00:02:17,060
Factory direct down jackets!

18
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,800
100 yuan each!

19
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,920
Clearance sale!

20
00:02:20,600 --> 00:02:21,720
Clearance sale!

21
00:02:22,160 --> 00:02:24,020
Once they're gone, they're gone!

22
00:02:24,200 --> 00:02:25,860
Factory direct down jackets!

23
00:02:27,560 --> 00:02:28,490
How much for one?

24
00:02:29,120 --> 00:02:30,400
100 yuan each.

25
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:38,120
Young man,

26
00:02:38,600 --> 00:02:40,720
