29
00:02:44,280 --> 00:02:45,160
It's just that

30
00:02:45,160 --> 00:02:47,480
I need yuan right now.

31
00:02:47,560 --> 00:02:49,640
I can't use these at the moment.

32
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,240
Do you have any yuan?

33
00:02:51,240 --> 00:02:52,770
I only brought these today.

34
00:02:53,000 --> 00:02:54,860
If you won't take them, forget it.

35
00:02:55,280 --> 00:02:55,810
Brother.

36
00:02:56,120 --> 00:02:57,960
What's the exchange rate for these German marks?

37
00:02:57,960 --> 00:02:58,680
One to five.

38
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,660
Isn't that the standard rate?

39
00:03:01,560 --> 00:03:02,160
Young man,

40
00:03:02,520 --> 00:03:04,520
you just started doing business here, right?

41
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,250
Around here,

42
00:03:05,600 --> 00:03:06,960
German marks,

43
00:03:06,960 --> 00:03:08,280
US dollars and yuan

44
