45
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:11,040
Ask other vendors.

46
00:03:11,040 --> 00:03:12,440
Then you'll understand.

47
00:03:12,480 --> 00:03:13,440
And people here

48
00:03:13,440 --> 00:03:14,480
really like to accept

49
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:16,079
German marks and US dollars.

50
00:03:16,120 --> 00:03:16,800
And why is that?

51
00:03:16,800 --> 00:03:18,040
Because they hold their value.

52
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:19,300
Today it's one to five,

53
00:03:19,480 --> 00:03:21,480
but next month it might be one to six.

54
00:03:22,320 --> 00:03:23,180
Just take them.

55
00:03:23,680 --> 00:03:25,610
I'll exchange them for yuan later.

56
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:32,720
How about it?

57
00:03:32,720 --> 00:03:33,720
Want to exchange?

58
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,480
Yes.

59
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:42,060
You've never even seen marks before.

60
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:44,000
How are you doing business here?

61
00:03:45,920 --> 00:03:46,520
Young man,

62
00:03:46,800 --> 00:03:47,480
I'll

63
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,040
leave you my contact information.

64
00:03:49,040 --> 00:03:50,400
In the future, if anyone else

65
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:52,000
uses German marks or US dollars

66
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:53,160
to buy things from you,

67
00:03:53,160 --> 00:03:54,220
just give me a call.

68
00:03:54,600 --> 00:03:56,660
I'll exchange however much you have.

69
00:04:06,960 --> 00:04:08,820
Down jackets direct from factory

70
00:04:08,880 --> 00:04:10,200
100 yuan each.

71
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,200
US dollars.

72
00:04:12,440 --> 00:04:13,170
German marks

73
