and euros all accepted.

74
00:04:19,920 --> 00:04:22,050
I feel like the way you're staring at me

75
00:04:22,320 --> 00:04:24,250
is like saying goodbye to a corpse.

76
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:28,120
I actually think it feels like a funeral viewing too.

77
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:28,680
Then why

78
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:30,280
are you still looking at me like that?

79
00:04:30,280 --> 00:04:31,720
I'm just wondering,

80
00:04:32,680 --> 00:04:34,280
why you're so good at pool.

81
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:36,650
Are you a professional player?

82
00:04:39,360 --> 00:04:40,720
Just playing with you.

83
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:41,520
I think

84
00:04:41,880 --> 00:04:44,480
I should look professional at everything I do.

85
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:45,440
When we get out of here,

86
00:04:45,440 --> 00:04:46,880
let's talk more.

87
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,120
Talk about what?

88
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:49,760
Once I'm out, I'm going straight home.

89
00:04:49,760 --> 00:04:51,960
Don't want to stay here a minute longer.

90
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,840
Cui, I think you're a good guy.

91
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:59,360
I've decided to tell you a secret.

92
00:04:59,600 --> 00:05:00,280
Go ahead.

93
00:05:00,680 --> 00:05:02,680
My brothers are coming to rescue me.

94
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,880
We'll leave together when they do.

95
00:05:06,760 --> 00:05:08,400
Give it a rest, will you?

96
00:05:08,760 --> 00:05:09,440
I admit defeat.

97
00:05:09,440 --> 00:05:10,800
I'm telling the truth.

98
00:05:11,040 --> 00:05:12,200
After we get out,

99
00:05:12,880 --> 00:05:13,880
I'm definitely going to find Feifei

100
00:05:13,880 --> 00:05:15,480
and have a good talk with her.

101
00:05:15,520 --> 00:05:17,180
I mean, such a beautiful girl,

102
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:19,240
why is she doing this kind of work?

103
00:05:19,240 --> 00:05:20,680
You go talk to her.

104
00:05:20,680 --> 00:05:22,280
Can you let me have some peace

105
00:05:22,560 --> 00:05:23,360
please?

106
00:05:24,320 --> 00:05:25,920
Down jackets!

107
00:05:26,080 --> 00:05:27,800
Super thick down jackets!

108
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,730
Selling at a loss for just 100 yuan!

109
00:05:29,840 --> 00:05:32,640
Extra thick and extra warm!

110
00:05:33,120 --> 00:05:34,320
Down jackets!

111
00:05:36,680 --> 00:05:38,940
