00:27:21,520 --> 00:27:23,240
and the same people who fought with you.

588
00:27:23,240 --> 00:27:24,360
I'll take you to identify them.

589
00:27:24,360 --> 00:27:26,020
Why didn't you say so earlier?

590
00:27:26,720 --> 00:27:27,440
Well, we have

591
00:27:27,440 --> 00:27:29,100
our own procedures to follow.

592
00:27:29,280 --> 00:27:30,740
Why should I report to you?

593
00:27:31,720 --> 00:27:32,520
Aren't we friends?

594
00:27:32,520 --> 00:27:33,160
Let's go.

595
00:27:38,920 --> 00:27:39,480
Follow behind.

596
00:27:39,480 --> 00:27:40,340
Get in quickly.

597
00:27:43,520 --> 00:27:44,320
It's them.

598
00:27:44,920 --> 00:27:49,080
There he is.

599
00:27:57,560 --> 00:28:00,240
Can you please put in a good word for us?

600
00:28:01,240 --> 00:28:02,360
Please.

601
00:28:04,280 --> 00:28:05,160
I'm sorry.

602
00:28:06,120 --> 00:28:07,360
We know we were wrong.

603
00:28:07,720 --> 00:28:09,600
Please, I'm begging you.

604
00:28:13,920 --> 00:28:14,720
Please.

605
00:28:15,280 --> 00:28:15,810
Brother.

606
00:28:17,000 --> 00:28:17,530
Brother.

607
00:28:26,240 --> 00:28:26,960
But I

608
00:28:27,880 --> 00:28:28,320
No.

609
00:28:28,320 --> 00:28:29,850
already made my statement.

610
00:28:29,920 --> 00:28:30,320
I...

611
00:28:30,320 --> 00:28:30,640
No.

612
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:33,040
It's really a misunderstanding, brother.

613
00:28:35,920 --> 00:28:36,640
Xiaofei.

614
00:28:38,040 --> 00:28:38,840
Cui.

615
00:28:40,080 --> 00:28:41,080
Who's this idiot?

616
00:28:41,320 --> 00:28:42,320
Who are you calling an idiot?

617
00:28:42,320 --> 00:28:43,280
I'm talking about you.

618
00:28:43,280 --> 00:28:43,920
Got a problem with that?

619
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:44,480
Stop.

620
00:28:44,480 --> 00:28:45,520
Why are you hitting me?

621
00:28:45,520 --> 00:28:47,480
Would I hit you if you didn't hit me first?

622
00:28:47,480 --> 00:28:48,600
And you say I have a problem?

623
00:28:48,600 --> 00:28:49,880
Let's go another round then.

624
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:51,400
You think I'm scared of you?

625
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:52,840
Bring it on!

626
00:28:54,320 --> 00:28:55,120
Alright.

627
00:28:55,120 --> 00:28:55,960
Everyone calm down.

628
00:28:55,960 --> 00:28:57,200
This is a police station.

629
00:28:57,200 --> 00:28:58,520
Don't cause trouble here.

630
00:28:58,520 --> 00:28:59,080
Let's go.

631
00:28:59,560 --> 00:29:00,360
Stop.

632
00:29:01,320 --> 00:29:02,560
We're all friends here.

633
00:29:02,560 --> 00:29:03,640
Shake hands and make peace.

634
00:29:03,640 --> 00:29:04,440
Listen to me.

635
00:29:05,840 --> 00:29:06,720
Do me a favor.

636
00:29:07,760 --> 00:29:08,560
Cui,

637
00:29:08,600 --> 00:29:10,320
is this the troublemaker friend

638
00:29:10,320 --> 00:29:11,650
you were talking about?

639
00:29:13,600 --> 00:29:15,600
What do you mean by 'troublemaker'?

640
00:29:16,000 --> 00:29:17,120
You're both troublemakers.

641
00:29:17,120 --> 00:29:19,650
You'll definitely become friends. Trust me.

642
00:29:20,720 --> 00:29:21,520
Hey.

643
00:29:22,040 --> 00:29:23,640
How have you been these days?

644
00:29:24,200 --> 00:29:24,930
Pretty good.

645
00:29:25,800 --> 00:29:27,200
When are you coming back?

646
00:29:29,240 --> 00:29:31,040
It'll be a while longer.

647
00:29:31,440 --> 00:29:32,560
Come back soon.

648
00:29:35,520 --> 00:29:36,440
What's wrong?

649
00:29:36,640 --> 00:29:38,000
You seem down.

650
00:29:38,360 --> 00:29:39,090
No, I'm fine.

651
00:29:39,360 --> 00:29:40,360
That's good then.

652
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:41,260
Come home soon.

653
00:29:41,720 --> 00:29:43,600
Mengmeng and Erpang miss you.

654
00:29:44,280 --> 00:29:45,200
I miss them too.

655
00:29:46,040 --> 00:29:46,900
And you as well.

656
00:29:55,240 --> 00:29:56,320
How about

657
00:29:57,120 --> 00:29:59,320
you stay and start a business with me?

658
00:30:00,040 --> 00:30:01,570
After losing so much money,

659
00:30:01,800 --> 00:30:04,120
it's hard to face your wife.

660
00:30:05,360 --> 00:30:06,720
Just watch TV.

661
00:30:10,600 --> 00:30:12,160
What did you mean

662
00:30:13,000 --> 00:30:15,440
by 'troublemaker'?

663
00:30:16,520 --> 00:30:17,850
Figure it out yourself.

664
00:30:18,520 --> 00:30:19,440
Cui.

665
00:30:20,120 --> 00:30:21,840
You're amazing.

666
00:30:22,560 --> 00:30:23,560
How could you tell

667
00:30:23,560 --> 00:30:25,280
I was born premature?

668
00:30:26,000 --> 00:30:27,080
It's obvious.

669
00:30:27,080 --> 00:30:28,800
My mom said I was

670
00:30:28,800 --> 00:30:31,000
born a full month premature.

671
00:30:31,000 --> 00:30:32,000
Just one month?

672
00:30:32,320 --> 00:30:34,120
How long do you think it was?

673
00:30:34,120 --> 00:30:35,800
At least a month and a half.

674
00:30:36,240 --> 00:30:37,040
Really?

675
00:30:38,440 --> 00:30:40,520
I should go back and ask my mom.

676
00:30:44,360 --> 00:30:45,960
That guy who fought with me,

677
00:30:46,160 --> 00:30:48,400
is he the same as me?

678
00:30:48,440 --> 00:30:49,400
Yes, probably.

679
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:51,120
So he's also a month and a half?

680
00:30:51,360 --> 00:30:52,560
He must be two months.

681
00:30:53,160 --> 00:30:56,120
So is that good or bad?

682
00:30:57,040 --> 00:30:58,480
Alright, he's smart.

683
00:31:00,400 --> 00:31:02,280
Then he's smarter than me.

684
00:31:04,720 --> 00:31:06,180
You two are about the same.

685
00:31:47,640 --> 00:31:48,700
What are you doing?

686
00:31:49,320 --> 00:31:50,380
I need to go to work.

687
00:31:51,160 --> 00:31:52,000
What work?

688
00:31:55,680 --> 00:31:57,210
Where are you going to work?

689
00:31:57,600 --> 00:31:58,600
This is my job.

690
00:31:58,840 --> 00:32:00,170
After I earn some money,

691
00:32:00,600 --> 00:32:02,330
I'll buy canned food for Lao Liu

692
00:32:02,480 --> 00:32:03,440
and milk powder.

693
00:32:05,840 --> 00:32:06,960
If you have any problems, go to the police.

694
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:08,240
Isn't there a police phone?

695
00:32:08,240 --> 00:32:09,600
Come back in one piece.

696
00:32:12,320 --> 00:32:14,560
We'll go back once you're better.

697
00:32:18,120 --> 00:32:20,800
This whole trip with you,

698
00:32:21,360 --> 00:32:23,040
I haven't been any help,

699
00:32:24,680 --> 00:32:26,160
and I've cost you money.

700
00:32:28,000 --> 00:32:30,000
Don't talk like that, Liu.

701
00:32:32,080 --> 00:32:34,800
You got hurt because of me.

702
00:32:35,760 --> 00:32:36,840
Being alive

703
00:32:37,400 --> 00:32:39,260
is more important than anything.

704
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:43,240
Alive...

705
00:32:45,280 --> 00:32:46,840
Just being alive is good.

706
00:32:48,120 --> 00:32:49,080
Do you know

707
00:32:49,520 --> 00:32:51,880
what I want to do most?

708
00:32:52,080 --> 00:32:52,880
What is it?

709
00:32:54,360 --> 00:32:57,280
When I have money someday,

710
00:32:58,840 --> 00:33:01,680
I want to buy that hill next to my hometown,

711
00:33:01,760 --> 00:33:03,000
find myself a wife,

712
00:33:04,080 --> 00:33:05,880
and live up there together.

713
00:33:06,920 --> 00:33:08,720
I'll be the king of the mountain.

714
00:33:09,720 --> 00:33:12,960
I'll grow whatever I want.

715
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:16,520
I'll raise whatever animals I like.

716
00:33:16,520 --> 00:33:18,760
Everything there will be mine.

717
00:33:21,000 --> 00:33:23,840
Even if a rabbit appears on the hill someday,

718
00:33:24,760 --> 00:33:26,290
it will have my surname Liu.

719
00:33:33,040 --> 00:33:34,370
Where's the tattoo guy?

720
00:33:34,800 --> 00:33:35,840
He went out on his cart

721
00:33:35,840 --> 00:33:37,240
to buy you some milk powder

722
00:33:37,240 --> 00:33:38,970
and nutritional supplements.

723
00:33:46,800 --> 00:33:47,120
Hello?

724
00:33:47,120 --> 00:33:47,800
Hi,

725
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:49,120
are you Cui Guoming?

726
00:33:49,120 --> 00:33:49,650
Yes, I am.

727
00:33:50,040 --> 00:33:51,720
About that case you reported,

728
00:33:51,720 --> 00:33:53,560
the counterfeit Peruvian currency fraud,

729
00:33:53,560 --> 00:33:55,760
we've recovered your money.

730
00:33:55,760 --> 00:33:57,400
Come to our police station to sign,

731
00:33:57,400 --> 00:33:58,720
and collect your money.

732
00:33:58,720 --> 00:33:59,440
Great.

733
00:33:59,680 --> 00:34:01,160
Thank you very much.

734
00:34:23,719 --> 00:34:24,600
Here it comes.

735
00:34:24,920 --> 00:34:26,719
I've got 6 motorcycles again.

736
00:34:27,880 --> 00:34:30,010
But I don't have any down jackets left.

737
00:34:30,480 --> 00:34:33,120
Why is the store next door closed?

738
00:34:33,320 --> 00:34:34,239
No idea.

739
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:37,159
Yesterday a group of police officers

740
00:34:37,159 --> 00:34:38,199
took them away.

741
00:34:38,880 --> 00:34:41,239
It couldn't be because of illegal trafficking, could it?

742
00:34:41,239 --> 00:34:42,920
That's certainly possible.

743
00:34:45,159 --> 00:34:47,520
Were they trafficking for you?

744
00:34:56,880 --> 00:34:58,440
Alright. Today

745
00:34:58,840 --> 00:35:00,160
we're all going back home.

746
00:35:00,160 --> 00:35:01,480
You don't need to go pedal your rickshaw anymore.

747
00:35:01,480 --> 00:35:02,560
I'm not going back.

748
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:04,000
I'm staying here.

749
00:35:04,320 --> 00:35:06,080
Forget it.

750
00:35:07,000 --> 00:35:08,800
We're checking out of the room soon.

751
00:35:08,800 --> 00:35:09,930
Where will you stay?

752
00:35:10,000 --> 00:35:11,600
I've already found a place.

753
00:35:11,920 --> 00:35:13,240
90 yuan per month.

754
00:35:13,360 --> 00:35:14,520
I won't go back until

755
00:35:14,720 --> 00:35:16,250
I make something of myself.

756
00:35:22,920 --> 00:35:23,840
Go to sleep.

757
00:35:25,680 --> 00:35:26,680
Look at you,

758
00:35:27,280 --> 00:35:28,920
buying four of everything.

759
00:35:29,440 --> 00:35:30,840
Four chocolates.

760
00:35:31,520 --> 00:35:32,880
Four milk powders.

761
00:35:33,280 --> 00:35:34,880
Even four matryoshka dolls.

762
00:35:35,200 --> 00:35:37,260
You're really exhausting yourself.

763
00:35:38,920 --> 00:35:40,480
That's what keeps me going.

764
00:35:48,960 --> 00:35:50,360
[In Russian] Put it back.

765
00:35:51,200 --> 00:35:53,800
[In Russian] Don't touch if you're not buying.

766
00:35:56,560 --> 00:35:57,360
How much?

767
00:35:57,920 --> 00:35:58,920
[In Russian] 600.

768
00:36:02,840 --> 00:36:03,600
Take it, brother.

769
00:36:03,600 --> 00:36:04,720
There are foreign women over there.

770
00:36:04,720 --> 00:36:05,520
I bought it.

771
00:36:06,560 --> 00:36:07,080
Really?

772
00:36:07,920 --> 00:36:09,960
If you keep insulting your customers,

773
00:36:09,960 --> 00:36:10,920
you'll lose

774
00:36:10,920 --> 00:36:12,650
many business opportunities.

775
00:36:14,680 --> 00:36:16,210
[In Russian] Keep smiling.

776
00:36:28,720 --> 00:36:29,360
Cui.

777
00:36:29,840 --> 00:36:31,480
Is that the Soviet Union over there?

778
00:36:31,480 --> 00:36:32,810
It's called Russia now.

779
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:36,360
Even countries change their names.

780
00:36:37,160 --> 00:36:37,880
Look over there.

781
00:36:37,880 --> 00:36:40,080
Maybe we'll see some pretty girls.

782
00:36:43,840 --> 00:36:44,640
Cui.

783
00:36:46,080 --> 00:36:47,720
Let me speak from the heart.

784
00:36:48,760 --> 00:36:49,760
Thank you so much.

785
00:36:51,360 --> 00:36:52,920
I grew up without parents.

786
00:36:53,120 --> 00:36:55,180
Nobody treated me like a human being.

787
00:36:56,600 --> 00:36:58,000
I've lived for over 50 years.

788
00:36:58,000 --> 00:36:59,930
I've never received a gift before.

789
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:01,530
This is my first one.

790
00:37:01,560 --> 00:37:03,120
I really love this.

791
00:37:05,840 --> 00:37:07,160
You and Huo.

792
00:37:07,160 --> 00:37:08,560
You're both good people.

793
00:37:09,960 --> 00:37:11,040
The best people.

794
00:37:12,360 --> 00:37:14,000
I've ever met in my life.

795
00:37:14,400 --> 00:37:15,000
Really.

796
00:37:16,240 --> 00:37:16,800
Cui.

797
00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:19,200
In the future,

798
00:37:19,480 --> 00:37:21,340
what would you do if you had money?

799
00:37:26,280 --> 00:37:26,640
Well,

800
00:37:26,640 --> 00:37:27,960
I once

801
00:37:27,960 --> 00:37:30,420
promised my daughter I'd buy her a Xiali car.

802
00:37:31,160 --> 00:37:33,280
Then I lost my job.

803
00:37:33,320 --> 00:37:34,520
So that car

804
00:37:34,680 --> 00:37:35,610
never happened.

805
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:39,680
Now I finally have some money.

806
00:37:40,360 --> 00:37:42,560
But there are more children at home now.

807
00:37:42,600 --> 00:37:44,320
They're growing up fast.

808
00:37:45,600 --> 00:37:47,000
I need to buy them a villa

809
00:37:47,640 --> 00:37:49,800
and create better living conditions.

810
00:37:50,640 --> 00:37:52,280
Look at you.

811
00:37:52,560 --> 00:37:53,680
I don't mean to criticize,

812
00:37:53,680 --> 00:37:55,880
but you always think about others.

813
00:37:56,560 --> 00:37:58,560
When will you think about yourself?

814
00:38:03,520 --> 00:38:04,320
Do you know

815
00:38:04,600 --> 00:38:06,480
why I always protect Dada?

816
00:38:07,720 --> 00:38:08,640
Why?

817
00:38:09,480 --> 00:38:12,680
Because there's a Dada living in my heart too.

818
00:38:13,840 --> 00:38:15,640
He's so much like how I used to be.

819
00:38:16,000 --> 00:38:17,160
As life went on,

820
00:38:17,760 --> 00:38:19,880
I forgot about that Dada.

821
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:22,440
Now I'm

822
00:38:23,120 --> 00:38:25,480
almost forty,

823
00:38:25,480 --> 00:38:27,400
a man with a family to support.

824
00:38:27,760 --> 00:38:30,000
How can we afford to think about ourselves?

825
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:31,800
Why wouldn't you have the right?

826
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:33,480
I just remembered,

827
00:38:33,480 --> 00:38:35,940
when you go back, find a shop for Huo quickly.

828
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:37,970
I almost forgot about that.

829
00:38:53,200 --> 00:38:54,160
This one you're riding now is fine.

830
00:38:54,160 --> 00:38:55,200
Second only to me.

831
00:38:58,200 --> 00:38:58,920
We're here.

832
00:38:58,920 --> 00:38:59,720
Good.

833
00:39:03,680 --> 00:39:05,880
It's not too late to come with us now.

834
00:39:06,520 --> 00:39:08,560
What about this bike?

835
00:39:08,560 --> 00:39:09,360
Leave it.

836
00:39:12,920 --> 00:39:14,320
I have to make something of myself

837
00:39:14,320 --> 00:39:15,250
before I go back.

838
00:39:15,760 --> 00:39:16,720
With this?

839
00:39:20,000 --> 00:39:21,530
This is just the beginning.

840
00:39:21,920 --> 00:39:22,760
In a year,

841
00:39:23,400 --> 00:39:24,640
it will become a car.

842
00:39:25,560 --> 00:39:26,480
In three years,

843
00:39:27,440 --> 00:39:28,800
it will become a fleet.

844
00:39:29,080 --> 00:39:31,840
I thought it would become a train in three years.

845
00:39:33,360 --> 00:39:35,220
So are you still getting tattoos?

846
00:39:36,720 --> 00:39:37,920
Let's survive first.

847
00:39:38,640 --> 00:39:40,800
I'll get back to it when I recover.

848
00:39:44,120 --> 00:39:46,240
Brother, I've been thinking about a lot of things lately.

849
00:39:46,240 --> 00:39:47,480
I feel that before,

850
00:39:47,720 --> 00:39:49,320
I thought too simply

851
00:39:49,720 --> 00:39:51,000
and acted recklessly.

852
00:39:52,720 --> 00:39:54,520
Thank you for putting up with me.

853
00:39:55,800 --> 00:39:57,040
I wrote you a letter.

854
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:59,810
Open it when you have time tonight.

855
00:40:01,200 --> 00:40:02,760
I hope you can

856
00:40:02,760 --> 00:40:04,220
return home in glory soon.

857
00:40:05,680 --> 00:40:07,360
It's normal for men to brag.

858
00:40:08,040 --> 00:40:09,200
But a real man

859
00:40:09,480 --> 00:40:10,960
must follow through

860
00:40:11,320 --> 00:40:12,780
on every promise he makes.

861
00:40:13,640 --> 00:40:14,280
Take care.

862
00:40:15,520 --> 00:40:16,440
Take care.

863
00:40:20,040 --> 00:40:21,370
If you run into trouble,

864
00:40:21,960 --> 00:40:23,200
you can still call me.

865
00:40:57,920 --> 00:40:59,480
We're here.

866
00:41:01,800 --> 00:41:03,640
Thank you.

867
00:42:18,800 --> 00:42:19,920
Children.

868
00:42:19,920 --> 00:42:20,680
Guess what?

869
00:42:20,680 --> 00:42:22,240
I...

870
00:42:36,240 --> 00:42:37,400
What gives you the right to live in our home?

871
00:42:37,400 --> 00:42:38,360
By what right?

872
00:42:38,360 --> 00:42:39,360
You think because you're in your house

873
00:42:39,360 --> 00:42:40,480
you can bully us?

874
00:42:40,560 --> 00:42:42,920
You think you can do whatever you want in your house?

875
00:42:42,920 --> 00:42:44,240
Stop disrupting our studies.

876
00:42:44,240 --> 00:42:46,970
You're always interfering with our schoolwork.

877
00:42:54,280 --> 00:42:55,200
What's going on here?
